title: Foldable and Portable Multi-Purpose Laptop Table Stand/Study Table/Bed Table/Ergonomic & Rounded Edges/Non-Slip Legs/Engineered Wood/Color - Plain Light Blue
description:
About Product:-

  • Color: Light Plain Blue
  • Compatible For all Laptop

The steel feet are covered with black sponge for good anti-slip effect.
